ation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/visibleAnnotations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/visibleAnnotations","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The complete list of annotations associated with the receiver that are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"currently visible."}],"title":"visibleAnnotations","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/visibleannotations","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"visibleAnnotations","kind":"identifier"}]}}}